room_title: Escape room "The Lab" by Challenge Accepted in Chicago
room_description: You are a doctor involved in medical research. You, along with other research doctors from universities all over the world, have come for a tour of our research lab. Our lab is devoted to the study of deadly viruses in an effort to make the world a safer place. You enter the lab only to find that the recently fired, and quite unstable, Dr. Duvarie Little has trapped you in the lab with a bomb. Now all of the visiting doctors must disarm the bomb in order to save the world from a devastating release of the deadly viruses.
